name: PersonalLedger
0:
”Alexa open daily ledger”
”fifty rupees spent on tea on second june”
”get amount spent on tea for the month of June”
skdetail:
This skill contains: dynamic content.
Invocation Name: daily ledger
des: You can say Daily ledger to start interacting with the skill. Using this skill, you can add and track the daily expenses for every month over the year. To add the details of an expense, you can say like, fifty rupees spent on tea on second june. To retrieve the details, say like, get amount spent on tea for the month of June.
priv: The developer reported that this skill does not collect personal information.
